# Assumption: Default solar thermal collector assumed: 40 sqft, Roof Pitch,

Solar collector orientation is based on rooftop solar orientation for electric backup and assumed south-facing for fuel backup. If a solar thermal system has no secondary water heater or has a second solar thermal system, they are assumed to have electric backup.
